title: VA Indie Pop Playlist October 2013 - Beauty (Dutch Treat I2 XHQ)
description:
And a Beauty it is!

After I3 Insane (really), already the second indie playlist for October 2013. 30 of finest Folk & Pop tracks with a lot of angels in it.

Unique tracks don't join easily and it was hard to avoid an angels choir. People might have some issues with angels. So I tried to hide them a bit. But then again, how do you hide an angel.... Enjoy, its beautiful.
